1003
00:42:08,140 --> 00:42:09,380
I have an idea.

1004
00:42:13,740 --> 00:42:14,580
Ningyan,

1005
00:42:16,020 --> 00:42:18,500
bring me to meet Grand Princess.

1006
00:42:18,820 --> 00:42:20,420
I can be her slave.

1007
00:42:20,420 --> 00:42:22,620
If I can make her happy,

1008
00:42:22,820 --> 00:42:24,420
she won't ask you for poems.

1009
00:42:24,780 --> 00:42:26,660
Then you can focus on

1010
00:42:26,940 --> 00:42:29,020
the ones Cijiu needs for the Academy.

1011
00:42:29,100 --> 00:42:29,940
Right?

1012
00:42:30,980 --> 00:42:32,260
Let's continue, Cijiu.

1013
00:42:32,380 --> 00:42:33,260
Let me think.

1014
00:42:37,040 --> 00:42:38,620
"Read books or you'll regret it someday."

1015
00:42:38,620 --> 00:42:39,460
Write.

1016
00:42:40,020 --> 00:42:40,940
