1022
00:42:56,340 --> 00:42:57,500
Caiwei?

1023
00:42:58,140 --> 00:42:59,060
Do you need me?

1024
00:42:59,060 --> 00:42:59,900
Not me,

1025
00:42:59,900 --> 00:43:01,260
