1026
00:43:01,700 --> 00:43:02,900
He said he made progress

1027
00:43:02,900 --> 00:43:03,860
on your mirror.

1028
00:43:05,300 --> 00:43:06,140
Really?

1029
00:43:06,740 --> 00:43:07,820
Let's go.

1030
00:43:08,340 --> 00:43:09,940
Sure, let's go! Come on!

1031
00:43:09,940 --> 00:43:11,900
Hey, wait! What about the poems I need?

1032
00:43:12,140 --> 00:43:13,940
- Come back!
- Did you ride or use footwork?

1033
00:43:21,660 --> 00:43:23,180
What do you think, Mother?

1034
00:43:24,940 --> 00:43:26,300
Perfect!

1035
00:43:26,940 --> 00:43:28,180
This half shows

1036
00:43:28,420 --> 00:43:29,780
high literary attainments.

1037
00:43:30,460 --> 00:43:31,300
Lin'an,

1038
00:43:31,740 --> 00:43:34,540
where did you get such beautiful lines?

1039
00:43:35,460 --> 00:43:36,460
Well, Mother,

1040
00:43:36,580 --> 00:43:38,300
I found an aide earlier,

1041
00:43:38,300 --> 00:43:39,300
who's a great poet.

1042
00:43:39,300 --> 00:43:41,820
I've got plenty of such masterpieces.

1043
00:43:42,730 --> 00:43:44,740
Compared with Huaiqing's men,

1044
00:43:45,300 --> 00:43:46,340
