1045
00:43:48,980 --> 00:43:50,100
This poem is great.

1046
00:43:50,500 --> 00:43:51,340
Lin'an,

1047
00:43:51,380 --> 00:43:53,660
you must wow everyone at the Poetry Contest

1048
00:43:53,660 --> 00:43:55,180
to make your brother proud.

1049
00:43:55,740 --> 00:43:56,580
Look at you.

1050
00:43:56,620 --> 00:43:58,020
You've lost tons of weight.

1051
00:43:59,220 --> 00:44:00,060
My kitchen

1052
00:44:00,070 --> 00:44:03,340
happened to make your favorite Milk Cakes.

1053
00:44:03,420 --> 00:44:04,740
Have some.

1054
00:44:10,780 --> 00:44:11,620
It's good.

1055
00:44:13,100 --> 00:44:13,940
Chuntao,

1056
00:44:14,020 --> 00:44:15,260
fetch more later

1057
00:44:15,260 --> 00:44:16,380
for Lin'an.

1058
00:44:16,540 --> 00:44:17,380
Yes.

1059
00:44:18,820 --> 00:44:19,700
Thanks, Mother.

1060
00:44:22,940 --> 00:44:24,580
Mother hasn't given me gifts for a while.

1061
00:44:26,700 --> 00:44:28,580
She doesn't know

1062
00:44:29,460 --> 00:44:31,380
