1063
00:44:34,300 --> 00:44:36,140
Still, she cares about me.

1064
00:44:36,820 --> 00:44:38,740
Or she wouldn't give me these cakes.

1065
00:44:42,940 --> 00:44:44,060
I should thank Xu Qi'an.

1066
00:44:44,620 --> 00:44:45,460
He deserves rewards.

1067
00:44:46,740 --> 00:44:47,940
Where did he go today?

1068
00:44:49,220 --> 00:44:50,500
He stayed at home all day

1069
00:44:50,500 --> 00:44:52,100
without going to work.

1070
00:44:52,820 --> 00:44:55,580
According to his routine,

1071
00:44:55,780 --> 00:44:57,860
