1097
00:46:24,170 --> 00:46:25,450
♪I flipped through pages♪

1098
00:46:25,450 --> 00:46:26,890
♪Took all the words I could♪

1099
00:46:26,890 --> 00:46:29,250
♪Only to realize
that love is a mysterious fate♪

1100
00:46:29,250 --> 00:46:30,490
♪I am still just a disciple♪

1101
00:46:30,650 --> 00:46:32,810
♪Strange skills and tricks
can't compare to true love♪

1102
00:46:32,810 --> 00:46:34,890
♪I'd use the rivers as ink,
and swords as a pen♪

1103
00:46:34,890 --> 00:46:37,410
