♪Mastering the 36 strategies♪

1116
00:47:02,970 --> 00:47:04,610
♪Unfolding the scroll, I write your name♪

1117
00:47:04,610 --> 00:47:05,970
♪The heavens bear witness for me♪

1118
00:47:05,970 --> 00:47:07,290
♪The mountains move for you♪

1119
00:47:07,290 --> 00:47:09,570
♪My heart is only for you
with no more exceptions♪

1120
00:47:09,570 --> 00:47:12,610
♪Thousands of words♪

1121
00:47:12,610 --> 00:47:15,010
♪For you, I can become Li Bai♪

1122
